{"tid":1568913,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"《煲底相見》—戰友們的約定〈原曲：就算世界無童話〉","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T16:20:28.000Z","uid":50360,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a364f3bd5e6b859eeafad82f25fd2d0d03aba1e5","tid":1568913,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"「答應我，別發表死訊」，這是我第一句想到的歌詞。<br />\n<br />\n由6月9日開始一直走來，有好多戰友被捕，亦有戰友犧牲性命。很灰，很失望，很無力。我記得我們要齊上齊落，我記得我們約定光復之日，一起到煲底除下眼罩口罩，望清楚一起發夢的手足，互相擁抱對方。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n「為來日煲底相見，讓自由遍地裡開花」，我們一起見證光復之日。<br />\n<br />\n《煲底相見》MV：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TUjg1e_6f8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTUjg1e_6f8E&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXShZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=746bf658\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TUjg1e_6f8E</a>"},{"pid":"c3f55e751c215442e7b23de57a9d88238aadd01e","tid":1568913,"uid":50360,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"《煲底相見》<br />\n<br />\n原曲：就算世界無童話<br />\n改編填詞：山卡啦<br />\n<br />\n夢見那雙黑色眼睛<br />\n再與我  上陣來險境<br />\n夢見滿街瘋狗叫聲<br />\n答應了  別到新屋嶺<br />\n<br />\n若到某天感觸太慘<br />\n有戰友  有萬人分擔<br />\n未到抗爭的最終<br />\n答應我  別發表死訊<br />\n<br />\n(why I smile cos you make me smile)<br />\n如真相最終得不到看待<br />\n而血債永被活埋封蓋<br />\n如純良人們難被記載<br />\n犧牲的不可節哀<br />\n香港會更加悲哀<br />\n<br />\n望見戰友人齊嗎  脫下裝備會面他<br />\n為來日煲底相見  讓自由遍地裡開花<br />\n若答應我人齊嗎  約定煲下完成它<br />\n夢遊夢得心灰  也不准變卦<br />\n<br />\n(why I smile cos you make me smile)<br />\n良知作抗爭可得到體諒<br />\n誰勇武割蓆換成鼓掌<br />\n如遊行人們沿路碰上<br />\n一起高呼聲最響<br />\n黑色覺醒般伸張<br />\n<br />\n望見戰友人齊嗎  我用真面目示他<br />\n未來在煲底相見  盼望能夠共抱一下<br />\n若答應我人齊嗎  約定煲下完成它<br />\n望能復興香港  那天不再怕<br />\n<br />\n(why I smile cos you make me smile)<br />\n夢見手足一起唱歌  我發覺  快樂才不多<br />\n直到某天煲底脫裝  人人能同座"},{"pid":"a0d230a26366dab81f3eaca6a9ff1e383af9fa4f","tid":1568913,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7c516c4fac994eb2d326d442bac21c83061cc986","tid":1568913,"uid":180431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:26:53.000Z","msg":"手足加油"},{"pid":"970858f9c31567fd72d81e7f47cad07fe3ba53fc","tid":1568913,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c516c4fac994eb2d326d442bac21c83061cc986","tid":1568913,"uid":180431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:26:53.000Z","msg":"手足加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:37:30.000Z","msg":"一齊加油﹗"},{"pid":"d7fa4ad87d6bbc9122e6a07356ec6053a91f1897","tid":1568913,"uid":314633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"不得了 眼濕濕😂 約實你啊 一定要係煲底見!!!"},{"pid":"9c4c4a76d190a1a7a79ac9fa2d599dadfd51212b","tid":1568913,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7fa4ad87d6bbc9122e6a07356ec6053a91f1897","tid":1568913,"uid":314633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"不得了 眼濕濕😂 約實你啊 一定要係煲底見!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"煲底見﹗"},{"pid":"7b7e777971380617b410535747d32d83f42e6729","tid":1568913,"uid":49767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:25:13.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"e92319a672a3bbf943429d4e6ff86f71ab7cd1f5","tid":1568913,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b7e777971380617b410535747d32d83f42e6729","tid":1568913,"uid":49767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:25:13.000Z","msg":"加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:02:15.000Z","msg":"一齊加油"},{"pid":"c4737c0d3af8cfbbb855b71298fd8df318fd89e6","tid":1568913,"uid":49767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:02:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dbda64ff2a4d9c1466ccfdc8babc1ffeb56ea828","tid":1568913,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4737c0d3af8cfbbb855b71298fd8df318fd89e6","tid":1568913,"ui